title: Phil Jamieson from Caspian
itunes:title: Phil Jamieson from Caspian
description:
Happy Thanksgiving (or one day after)! Here is a holiday treat for all of you fine people in internet land, my discussion with Phil from Caspian. He plays guitar in the band and while the band is primarily instrumental, he has a lot of things to say. We discuss being introspective, finding the right fit and work ethic. Phil was ready to go deep, and we went there with him. Hope you enjoy! - - - -This weeks show is brought to you by Zevia, the clear, zero calorie soda that tastes amazing!This weeks show is ALSO brought to you by Title Fight and their full length, HYPERVIEWFollow the show on TwitterEmail the show!
